sn_aia_skill_metadata.description: Automates the process of updating and maintaining bucket choices for defects in the GAIC Defect table. Designed for administrators or process owners who need to efficiently manage defect categorization and ensure each defect is assigned to the correct bucket without duplicating existing choices.
sn_aia_skill_metadata.name: Defect Choice Agent
